## AI & Security Disclaimer

This project includes an AI-based assistant designed to provide responses
based on predefined documentation using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).

Important considerations:

- The system is intended for informational and support purposes only.
- It MUST NOT be used to expose or manage sensitive information such as:
  credentials, tokens, internal IPs, infrastructure details, or security configurations.
- AI-generated responses may be incomplete or inaccurate.

The author assumes no responsibility for:

- Misuse of the software
- Security vulnerabilities due to improper deployment
- Decisions made based on AI-generated outputs

Users are solely responsible for securing:

- API keys and tokens
- Telegram bot credentials
- Infrastructure and deployment environments

